# CORS proxy URL for the Haskell Playground API.
# Required because play.haskell.org doesn't support CORS from browser origins.
#
# Deploy the Cloudflare Worker in proxy/ then set this to your worker URL:
#   npx wrangler deploy proxy/worker.js --name categorical-proxy
#
# Example:
# VITE_PLAYGROUND_PROXY_URL=https://categorical-proxy.YOUR_SUBDOMAIN.workers.dev
